  shows "x âˆˆ set b"

  unfolding lin_sat_def by auto

definition wits :: "'a branch â‡’ 'a set" where
  "wits b â‰¡ vars b - vars (last b)"

definition pwits :: "'a branch â‡’ 'a set" where
  "pwits b â‰¡ {c âˆˆ wits b. âˆ€t âˆˆ subterms (last b).
                  AT (Var c =â‡©s t) âˆ‰ set b âˆ§ AT (t =â‡©s Var c) âˆ‰ set b}"

lemma wits_singleton[simp]: "wits [Ï†] = {}"
  unfolding wits_def vars_branch_simps by simp

lemma pwits_singleton[simp]: "pwits [Ï†] = {}"
  unfolding pwits_def by auto

lemma pwitsD:
  assumes "c âˆˆ pwits b"
  shows "c âˆˆ wits b"
        "t âˆˆ subterms (last b) âŸ¹ AT (Var c =â‡©s t) âˆ‰ set b"
        "t âˆˆ subterms (last b) âŸ¹ AT (t =â‡©s Var c) âˆ‰ set b"

lemma lexpands_subterms_branch_eq:
  "lexpands b' b âŸ¹ b â‰  [] âŸ¹ subterms (b' @ b) = subterms b"
proof(induction rule: lexpands.induct)
  case (1 b' b)
  then show ?case
    apply(induction rule: lexpands_fm.induct)
         apply(auto simp: subterms_branch_def)
    done
next
  case (2 b' b)
  then show ?case
    apply(induction rule: lexpands_un.induct)
    using subterms_branch_subterms_subterms_fm_trans[OF _ subterms_refl]
         apply(auto simp: subterms_branch_simps 
          intro: subterms_term_subterms_branch_trans
          dest: subterms_branchD AT_mem_subterms_branchD AF_mem_subterms_branchD)
    done
next
  case (3 b' b)
  then show ?case
    apply(induction rule: lexpands_int.induct)
    using subterms_branch_subterms_subterms_fm_trans[OF _ subterms_refl]
         apply(auto simp: subterms_branch_simps 
          intro: subterms_term_subterms_branch_trans
          dest: subterms_branchD AT_mem_subterms_branchD AF_mem_subterms_branchD)
    done
next
  case (4 b' b)
  then show ?case
    apply(induction rule: lexpands_diff.induct)
    using subterms_branch_subterms_subterms_fm_trans[OF _ subterms_refl]
         apply(auto simp: subterms_branch_simps 
          intro: subterms_term_subterms_branch_trans
          dest: subterms_branchD AT_mem_subterms_branchD AF_mem_subterms_branchD)
    done
next
  case (5 b' b)
  then show ?case
  proof(induction rule: lexpands_single.induct)
    case (1 t1 b)
    then show ?case
      using subterms_branch_subterms_subterms_fm_trans[OF _ subterms_refl]
      apply(auto simp: subterms_branch_simps
            dest: subterms_fmD intro: subterms_term_subterms_branch_trans)
      done
  qed (auto simp: subterms_branch_simps subterms_term_subterms_atom_Atom_trans
       dest: subterms_branchD AF_mem_subterms_branchD 
       intro: subterms_term_subterms_branch_trans)
next
  case (6 b' b)
  have *: "subterms_atom (subst_tlvl t1 t2 a) âŠ† subterms t2 âˆª subterms_atom a"
    for t1 t2 and a :: "'a pset_atom"
    by (cases "(t1, t2, a)" rule: subst_tlvl.cases) auto
  from 6 show ?case
  by (induction rule: lexpands_eq.induct)
     (auto simp: subterms_branch_def subterms_term_subterms_atom_Atom_trans
            dest!: subsetD[OF *])
qed

lemma lexpands_vars_branch_eq:
  "lexpands b' b âŸ¹ b â‰  [] âŸ¹ vars (b' @ b) = vars b"
  using lexpands_subterms_branch_eq subterms_branch_eq_if_vars_branch_eq by metis

lemma bexpands_nowit_subterms_branch_eq:
  "bexpands_nowit bs' b âŸ¹ b' âˆˆ bs' âŸ¹ b â‰  [] âŸ¹ subterms (b' @ b) = subterms b"

    by (auto simp: subterms_term_subterms_atom_Atom_trans subterms_branch_simps)

  case (4 s t1 b t2)
  then show ?case
    using subterms_branch_subterms_subterms_fm_trans[OF _ _ "4"(2)]
    by (auto simp: subterms_term_subterms_atom_Atom_trans subterms_branch_simps)

  case (5 s t1 b t2)
  then show ?case
    using subterms_branch_subterms_subterms_fm_trans[OF _ _ "5"(2)]
    by (auto simp: subterms_term_subterms_atom_Atom_trans subterms_branch_simps)
qed (use subterms_branch_def in â€¹(fastforce simp: subterms_branch_simps)+â€º)

lemma Var_mem_subterms_branch_and_not_in_wits:
  assumes "Var v âˆˆ subterms b" "v âˆ‰ wits b"
  shows "v âˆˆ vars (last b)"

lemma subterms_branch_cases:
  assumes "t âˆˆ subterms b" "t âˆ‰ Var ` wits b"
  obtains
    (Empty) n where "t = âˆ… n"
  | (Union) t1 t2 where "t = t1 âŠ”â‡©s t2"
  | (Inter) t1 t2 where "t = t1 âŠ“â‡©s t2"
  | (Diff) t1 t2 where "t = t1 -â‡©s t2"
  | (Single) t1 where "t = Single t1"
  | (Var) v where "t = Var v" "v âˆˆ vars (last b)"
proof(cases t)
  case (Var x)
  with assms have "x âˆˆ vars (last b)"
    using Var_mem_subterms_branch_and_not_in_wits by (metis imageI)
  with Var that show ?thesis by blast
qed (use assms that in auto)

lemma no_new_subterms_casesI[case_names Empty Union Inter Diff Single]:
  assumes "â‹€n. âˆ… n âˆˆ subterms b âŸ¹ âˆ… n âˆˆ subterms (last b)"
  assumes "â‹€t1 t2. t1 âŠ”â‡©s t2 âˆˆ subterms b âŸ¹ t1 âŠ”â‡©s t2 âˆˆ subterms (last b)"
  assumes "â‹€t1 t2. t1 âŠ“â‡©s t2 âˆˆ subterms b âŸ¹ t1 âŠ“â‡©s t2 âˆˆ subterms (last b)"
  assumes "â‹€t1 t2. t1 -â‡©s t2 âˆˆ subterms b âŸ¹ t1 -â‡©s t2 âˆˆ subterms (last b)"
  assumes "â‹€t. Single t âˆˆ subterms b âŸ¹ Single t âˆˆ subterms (last b)"
  shows "no_new_subterms b"
proof(intro no_new_subtermsI)
  fix t assume "t âˆˆ subterms b" "t âˆ‰ Var ` wits b"
  with this assms show "t âˆˆ subterms (last b)"
    by (cases t rule: subterms_branch_cases) (auto simp: vars_fm_subs_subterms_fm)
qed

lemma no_new_subtermsD:

lemma card_realisation:
  "hcard (realise t) â‰¤ 2 * card (subterms b)"
proof(induction t rule: realise.induct)
  case (1 x)
  then have "hcard (realise x) = card (realise ` parents (bgraph b) x âˆª {I x})"
    using hcard_HF Zero_hf_def parents_empty_if_base_vars by simp
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ card (realise ` parents (bgraph b) x) + card {I x}"
    using card_Un_le by blast
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ card (parents (bgraph b) x) + 1"
    using card_image_le[OF fin_digraph_bgraph.finite_parents]
    by auto
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ card (subterms b) + card {x}"
    using fin_digraph_bgraph.parents_subs_verts[unfolded verts_bgraph_eq_subterms]
    using card_mono[OF finite_subterms_branch]
    by (simp add: "1.hyps" not_dominated_if_base_vars)
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ card (subterms b) + card ({x} âˆª subterms b)"
    apply (intro add_le_mono card_mono[where ?B="{x} âˆª subterms b"])
    using finite_subterms_branch by auto
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ 2 * card (subterms b)"
  proof -
    from 1 have "x âˆˆ subterms b"
      using "1.prems" verts_bgraph verts_bgraph_eq_subterms wf_branch_not_Nil[OF wf_branch]
      by blast
    then show ?thesis
      unfolding mult_2 by (metis insert_absorb insert_is_Un order_refl)
  qed
  finally show ?case .
next
  case (2 t)
  then have "hcard (realise t) = card (realise ` parents (bgraph b) t)"
    using hcard_HF[OF finite_realisation_parents] by simp
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ card (parents (bgraph b) t)"
    using card_image_le by blast
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ card (subterms b)"
    using fin_digraph_bgraph.parents_subs_verts wf_branch_not_Nil[OF wf_branch]
    unfolding verts_bgraph_eq_subterms
    by (metis card_mono fin_digraph_bgraph.finite_verts verts_bgraph_eq_subterms)
  finally show ?case
    unfolding base_vars_Un_subterms'_eq_subterms by auto
next
  case (3 t)
  then show ?case by simp
qed

lemma bexpands_not_literal_mem_subfms_last:
  defines "P â‰¡ (Î»b. âˆ€Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. Â¬ is_literal Ïˆ

lemma expandss_not_literal_mem_subfms_last:

lemma card_not_literal_branch_if_wf_branch:
  assumes "wf_branch b"
  shows "card {Ï† âˆˆ set b. Â¬ is_literal Ï†} â‰¤ 2 * card (subfms (last b))"
proof -
  from assms obtain Ï† where "expandss b [Ï†]"
    unfolding wf_branch_def by blast
  then have [simp]: "last b = Ï†"
    by simp
  have "{Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. Â¬ is_literal Ïˆ} âŠ† subfms Ï† âˆª Neg ` subfms Ï†"
    using expandss_not_literal_mem_subfms_last[OF â€¹expandss b [Ï†]â€º]
    by auto
  from card_mono[OF _ this] have
    "card {Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. Â¬ is_literal Ïˆ} â‰¤ card (subfms Ï† âˆª Neg ` subfms Ï†)"
    using finite_subfms finite_imageI by fast
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ card (subfms Ï†) + card (Neg ` subfms Ï†)"
    using card_Un_le by blast
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ 2 * card (subfms Ï†)"
    unfolding mult_2 by (simp add: card_image_le finite_subfms)
  finally show ?thesis
    by simp
qed

lemma card_wf_branch_ub:
  assumes "wf_branch b"
  shows "card (set b)
      â‰¤ 2 * card (subfms (last b)) + 16 * (card (subterms (last b)))^4"
proof -
  let ?csts = "card (subterms (last b))"
  have "set b = {Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. Â¬ is_literal Ïˆ} âˆª {Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. is_literal Ïˆ}"
    by auto
  then have "card (set b)
    = card ({Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. Â¬ is_literal Ïˆ}) + card ({Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. is_literal Ïˆ})"
    using card_Un_disjoint finite_Un
    by (metis (no_types, lifting) List.finite_set disjoint_iff mem_Collect_eq)
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ 2 * card (subfms (last b)) + 4 * (?csts + card (wits b))â‡§2"
    using assms card_literals_branch_if_wf_branch card_not_literal_branch_if_wf_branch
    by fastforce
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ 2 * card (subfms (last b)) + 4 * (?csts + ?cstsâ‡§2)â‡§2"
    using assms card_wits_ub_if_wf_branch by auto
  also have "â€¦ â‰¤ 2 * card (subfms (last b)) + 16 * ?csts^4"
  proof -
    have "1 â‰¤ ?csts"
      using finite_subterms_fm[THEN card_0_eq]
      by (auto intro: Suc_leI)
    then have "(?csts + ?cstsâ‡§2)â‡§2 = ?cstsâ‡§2 + 2 * ?csts^3 + ?csts^4"
      by algebra
    also have "â€¦ â‰¤ ?cstsâ‡§2 + 2 * ?csts^4 + ?csts^4"
      using power_increasing[OF _ â€¹1 â‰¤ ?cstsâ€º] by simp
    also have "â€¦ â‰¤ ?csts^4 + 2 * ?csts^4 + ?csts^4"
      using power_increasing[OF _ â€¹1 â‰¤ ?cstsâ€º] by simp
    also have "â€¦ â‰¤ 4 * ?csts^4"
      by simp
    finally show ?thesis
      by simp
  qed
  finally show ?thesis .
qed

locale mlss_proc =
  fixes lexpand :: "'a branch â‡’ 'a branch"
  assumes lexpands_lexpand:
    "Â¬ lin_sat b âŸ¹ lexpands (lexpand b) b âˆ§ set b âŠ‚ set (lexpand b @ b)"
  fixes bexpand :: "'a branch â‡’ 'a branch set"
  assumes bexpands_bexpand:
    "Â¬ sat b âŸ¹ lin_sat b âŸ¹ bexpands (bexpand b) b"

function (domintros) mlss_proc_branch :: "'a branch â‡’ bool" where
  "Â¬ lin_sat b
  âŸ¹ mlss_proc_branch b = mlss_proc_branch (lexpand b @ b)"
| "âŸ¦ lin_sat b; bclosed b âŸ§ âŸ¹ mlss_proc_branch b = True"

  âŸ¹ mlss_proc_branch b = (âˆ€b' âˆˆ bexpand b. mlss_proc_branch (b' @ b))"

  by auto

lemma mlss_proc_branch_dom_if_wf_branch:
  assumes "wf_branch b"
  shows "mlss_proc_branch_dom b"
proof -
  define card_ub :: "'a branch â‡’ nat" where
    "card_ub â‰¡ Î»b. 2 * card (subfms (last b)) + 16 * (card (subterms (last b)))^4"
  from assms show ?thesis
  proof(induction "card_ub b - card (set b)"
      arbitrary: b rule: less_induct)
    case less
    have less': "mlss_proc_branch_dom b'" if "set b âŠ‚ set b'" "expandss b' b" for b'
    proof -
      note expandss_last_eq[OF â€¹expandss b' bâ€º wf_branch_not_Nil[OF â€¹wf_branch bâ€º]] 
      then have "card_ub b' = card_ub b"
        unfolding card_ub_def by simp
      moreover from that â€¹wf_branch bâ€º have "wf_branch b'"
        by (meson expandss_trans wf_branch_def)
      ultimately have "mlss_proc_branch_dom b'" if "card (set b') > card (set b)"
        using less(1)[OF _ â€¹wf_branch b'â€º] card_wf_branch_ub that
        by (metis (no_types, lifting) card_ub_def diff_less_mono2 order_less_le_trans)
      with that show ?thesis
        by (simp add: psubset_card_mono)
    qed
    then show ?case
    proof(cases "sat b")
      case False
      then consider
        b' where  "Â¬ lin_sat b" "lexpands b' b" "set b âŠ‚ set (b' @ b)" |
        bs' where "lin_sat b" "Â¬ sat b" "bexpands bs' b" "bs' â‰  {}"
                  "âˆ€b' âˆˆ bs'. set b âŠ‚ set (b' @ b)"
        unfolding sat_def lin_sat_def
        using bexpands_strict_mono bexpands_nonempty
        by (metis (no_types, opaque_lifting) inf_sup_aci(5) psubsetI set_append sup_ge1)
      then show ?thesis
      proof(cases)
        case 1
        with less' show ?thesis 
          using mlss_proc_branch.domintros(1)
          by (metis expandss.intros(1,2) lexpands_lexpand)
      next
        case 2
        then show ?thesis
          using less' bexpands_bexpand mlss_proc_branch.domintros(2,3)
          by (metis bexpands_strict_mono expandss.intros(1,3))
      qed
    qed (use mlss_proc_branch.domintros(4) sat_def in metis)
  qed
qed

lemma mlss_proc_branch_complete:
  fixes b :: "'a branch"
  assumes "wf_branch b"
  assumes "Â¬ mlss_proc_branch b"
  assumes "infinite (UNIV :: 'a set)"
  shows "âˆƒM. interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M (last b)"
proof -
  from mlss_proc_branch_dom_if_wf_branch[OF assms(1)] assms(1,2,3)
  show ?thesis
  proof(induction rule: mlss_proc_branch.pinduct)
    case (1 b)
    let ?b' = "lexpand b"
    from 1 lexpands_lexpand have "wf_branch (?b' @ b)"
      using wf_branch_lexpands by blast
    moreover from 1 lexpands_lexpand have "Â¬ mlss_proc_branch (?b' @ b)"
      by (simp add: mlss_proc_branch.psimps)
    ultimately obtain M where "interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M (last (?b' @ b))"
      using 1 by auto
    with 1 show ?case
      using wf_branch_not_Nil by auto
  next
    case (2 b)
    then show ?case by (simp add: mlss_proc_branch.psimps)
  next
    case (3 b)
    let ?bs' = "bexpand b"
    from 3 bexpands_bexpand obtain b' where b': "b' âˆˆ ?bs'" "Â¬ mlss_proc_branch (b' @ b)"
      using mlss_proc_branch.psimps(3) by metis
    with 3 bexpands_bexpand have "wf_branch (b' @ b)"
      using wf_branch_expandss[OF â€¹wf_branch bâ€º expandss.intros(3)]
      using expandss.intros(1) by blast
    with 3 b' obtain M where "interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M (last (b' @ b))"
      by auto
    with 3 show ?case
      by auto
  next
    case (4 b)
    then have "bopen b"
      by (simp add: mlss_proc_branch.psimps)
    interpret open_branch b
      using â€¹wf_branch bâ€º â€¹bopen bâ€º â€¹infinite UNIVâ€º
      by unfold_locales assumption+
    from coherence[OF â€¹sat bâ€º last_in_set] show ?case
      using wf_branch wf_branch_not_Nil by blast
  qed
qed

lemma mlss_proc_branch_sound:
  assumes "wf_branch b"
  assumes "âˆ€Ïˆ âˆˆ set b. interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M Ïˆ"
  shows "Â¬ mlss_proc_branch b"

  assume "mlss_proc_branch b"
  with mlss_proc_branch_dom_if_wf_branch[OF â€¹wf_branch bâ€º]
  have "âˆƒb'. expandss b' b âˆ§ (âˆƒM. âˆ€Ïˆ âˆˆ set b'. interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M Ïˆ) âˆ§ bclosed b'"
    using assms
  proof(induction arbitrary: M rule: mlss_proc_branch.pinduct)
    case (1 b)
    let ?b' = "lexpand b"
    from 1 lexpands_lexpand â€¹wf_branch bâ€º have "wf_branch (?b' @ b)"
      using wf_branch_lexpands by metis
    with 1 lexpands_sound lexpands_lexpand obtain b'' where
      "expandss b'' (?b' @ b)" "âˆƒM. âˆ€Ïˆ âˆˆ set b''. interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M Ïˆ" "bclosed b''"
      by (fastforce simp: mlss_proc_branch.psimps)
    with 1 lexpands_lexpand show ?case
      using expandss_trans expandss.intros(1,2) by meson
  next
    case (3 b)
    let ?bs' = "bexpand b"
    from 3 â€¹wf_branch bâ€º bexpands_bexpand have wf_branch_b':
      "wf_branch (b' @ b)" if "b' âˆˆ ?bs'" for b'
      using that expandss.intros(3) wf_branch_def by metis
    from bexpands_sound bexpands_bexpand 3 obtain M' b' where
      "b' âˆˆ ?bs'" "âˆ€Ïˆ âˆˆ set (b' @ b). interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M' Ïˆ"
      by metis
    with "3.IH" â€¹mlss_proc_branch bâ€º wf_branch_b' obtain b'' where
      "b' âˆˆ ?bs'" "expandss b'' (b' @ b)"
      "âˆƒM. âˆ€Ïˆ âˆˆ set b''. interp Iâ‡©sâ‡©a M Ïˆ" "bclosed b''"
      using mlss_proc_branch.psimps(3)[OF "3.hyps"(2-4,1)] by blast
    with 3 bexpands_bexpand show ?case
      using expandss_trans expandss.intros(1,3) by metis
  qed (use expandss.intros(1) mlss_proc_branch.psimps(4) in â€¹blast+â€º)
  with bclosed_sound show False by blast
qed
